orage only for projection exports/backups, repo cache rebuildable, per-repo locks, `gc.auto=0`, Git maintenance only under lock.**","tool_name":null,"tool_input":null,"source_record":{"timestamp":"2026-05-24T16:13:27.778Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"message","role":"assistant","phase":"final_answer"}}}